          We understand VA Minimum Property Requirements (MPRs) and work closely with VA-experienced appraisers to support a smooth valuation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-comments-dollar text-3xl text-[#5c3f14] mb-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
